.{}.  Secret Cache  (Stealth ability)

Resources:  20 lumber, 6 nails, 20 blocks, 5 imperium ingots
Built on:  plains, desert
Chameleon:  &g....&0 or &Y....&0

This ability allows you to build the secret cache, a place to store your
