#
SHADOWCAGE "SHADOW CAGE"

Shadowcage
Class ability: Occultist
Debuff type: Stealth
Cost: 50 move
Cooldown: 30 seconds

You create a cage of shadows, penalizing all enemies. The first victim loses
dodge equal to 5x your Charisma. Each additional victim loses dodge equal to 3x
